mpleted \n\n\u2022  Start of Care \n\n\u2022  Resumption of Care  \n\n\u2022  Discharge from agency \n\nOASIS-E1 \nEffective 01/01/2025 \nCenters for Medicare & Medicaid Services \n\n79\n\fChapter 3 \n\nResponse-Specific Instructions \n\nSection C: Cognitive Patterns \n\nIf SOC/ROC assessment, complete as close to the time of SOC/ROC as possible. If discharge assessment, \ncomplete as close to the time of discharge as possible.", "type": "Document"}}